data.description: Your dream home awaits with a $10000 seller credit for buyers closing costs.  No HOA! Elevate your lifestyle at 3331 Fairway Drive—a perfect haven! This 4-bed, 3.5-bath home spans 2911 sq ft. This home has abundant space! The backyard is a peaceful escape with mature trees and a lawn. Solar panel system helps with the awful NV energy rates. Easy to view. Reach out to listing agent today to schedule an appointment! Downstairs being painted on 10/26.
